text: Pablo Elier Sánchez Salgado is a Cuban football manager, currently managing Cuba. ==Managerial career== From 2013 to 2018, Sánchez was manager of Cuban club Pinar del Río. In July 2019, Sánchez was appointed manager of Cuba after previously being in a physical trainer capacity for the country. ==References== Category:Date of birth missing (living people) Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Cuba national football team managers Category:Cuban football managers
